com.datastax.dse.driver.api.core.data.geometry

Interface Polygon

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Geometry

    public interface Polygon
extends Geometry
    The driver-side representation of DSE's Polygon.

    This is a planar surface in a two-dimensional XY-plane, represented by one exterior boundary and 0 or more interior boundaries.

    The default implementation returned by the driver is immutable.

      • builder

        @NonNull
static Polygon.Builder builder()
        Returns a polygon builder.

        This is intended for complex polygons with multiple rings (i.e. holes inside the polygon). For simple cases, consider fromPoints(Point, Point, Point, Point...) instead.
